[div class=p 
	"Metro-Cross is a 1985 arcade game by Namco about the Runner running and jumping to the right for what I assume is glory since there's not really a plot otherwise. Across 32 rounds, the runner must avoid obstacles littering Metro and Cross the finish line before time runs out.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"I was playing some Namco Museum games on the Playstation recently and Metro-Cross caught my attention. While I'm not exactly good at it, I was intrigued enough to want to TAS it and learn more about it.
	$LF
]div
